OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent Rachel Younger,
OL,7,FProducer Aisha Kherallah and Cameraman
OL,8,FJake Langtree travelled with three-
OL,9,Fyear-old Ahmad from Egypt to Italy, as
OL,10,Fhis uncle shared with them his
OL,11,Fnephew's tragic experience of the war
OL,12,Fin Gaza
OL,14,FThree-year-old Ahmad Shabbat has never
OL,15,Fbeen on a plane.
OL,17,FHe only knows the frightening roar of
OL,18,FIsraeli F16 jets which have been
OL,19,Frelentlessly bombing his homeland.
