OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FOver the past seven months airstrikes
OL,7,Fon Gaza have killed Ahmad's mum and
OL,8,Fdad and his big brother Mohammed. His
OL,9,Flegs are gone too, amputated back in
OL,10,FNovember.
OL,12,FUndaunted, he speeds around Cairo
OL,13,Fairport, handling his electric
OL,14,Fwheelchair like a dodgem.
OL,16,FHaving made it across the border to
OL,17,FEgypt, Ahmad is heading to Italy for
OL,18,Fmedical treatment on the first private
OL,19,Frescue flight to Europe, run by
OL,20,FBritish charity .
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/14
