OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FGetting him out of Gaza has involved
OL,7,Fhours of work by the international
OL,8,Fteam of women at . They've lobbied
OL,9,Fembassies, governments and consulates
OL,10,Fto get Ahmad his passport, permits and
OL,11,Fpapers.
OL,13,FITV News is travelling with him and
OL,14,Fover the next few hours, his uncle
OL,15,Fshares Ahmad's story. It soon becomes
OL,16,Fclear that it is also the story of
OL,17,Fthis war, from the very first night it
OL,18,Fhit Gaza.
