OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FIn the northeastern town of Beit
OL,7,FHanoun, Ahmad, known for his cheeky
OL,8,Fsmile, is starting to get excited
OL,9,Fabout his first day at nursery.
OL,11,FHe is looking forward to joining his
OL,12,Fbig brother Mohammed on the daily walk
OL,13,Fto school.
OL,15,FAs news of Hamas' assault on Israel
OL,16,Fbegins to emerge, the Shabbat family,
OL,17,Flike everyone else in Gaza, brace for
OL,18,FIsrael's response.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
