OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FBy October 10, Beit Hanoun, the only
OL,7,Fplace Ahmed has ever called home, is
OL,8,Funrecognisable.
OL,10,FThe Israel Defence Forces (IDF) drop
OL,11,Fleaflets from the sky, warning those
OL,12,Fleft to move to safer areas.
OL,14,FNuseirat, a small town 16 kilometres
OL,15,Fsouth, is one of the areas listed. So,
OL,16,Fnow in the care of two of his uncles,
OL,17,FIbrahim and Salah, the toddler is
OL,18,Ftaken there in a bid to seek safety.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/14
