OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FThe stalls are hit by an Israeli
OL,7,Fmissile which blows off the three-year-
OL,8,Fold's legs.
OL,10,FHis uncle Saleh cannot keep the
OL,11,Fpromise he's made to raise Ahmad as
OL,12,Fhis own because he doesn't survive the
OL,13,Fblast.
OL,15,FAt Gaza's Al Aqsa hospital, surgeons
OL,16,Fexhausted by five weeks of treating
OL,17,Fthe wounded manage to save Ahmad's
OL,18,Flife.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/14
