OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FIbrahim has to make the agonising
OL,7,Fdecision to leave his wife and one-and-
OL,8,Fa-half year old daughter behind to get
OL,9,Fhis nephew out.
OL,11,FOnly after a direct plea to Egypt's
OL,12,Fpresident are the pair allowed to
OL,13,Fcross and head for a hospital that can
OL,14,Fhelp them in Cairo.
OL,16,FSomehow, thanks to the love and care
OL,17,Fof his uncle and the doctors and
OL,18,Fnurses who tend to his injuries, Ahmad
OL,19,Fstarts smiling again.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/14
