OL,3,CHe lost his family, then his legs: One
OL,4,Cchild's experience in Gaza
OL,6,FHe loves to race around the hospital
OL,7,Fcorridors, using a joystick to
OL,8,Fnavigate his new electric wheelchair,
OL,9,Fspeeding down hospital corridors.
OL,11,FAhmad needs prosthetic legs and Italy
OL,12,Fhas offered to take him in and provide
OL,13,Fhim with medical care, after the UK
OL,14,FHome Office refused him entry.
OL,16,FFor a boy who's brushed so close to
OL,17,Fdeath, Ahmad is bursting with life and
OL,18,Fmischief. But he still asks for his
OL,19,Fmum and sometimes screams at his uncle
OL,20,Fthat he wants his old legs back.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/14
